thanks.  i've read some of these but i've been looking for the issues i missed.
Based on the byte-size, issue #14 in this torrent is a broken version with a non-working page 14 ("Y_-_The_Last_Man_14_p13").
a hand full of the pages didn't work for me, but for the most part it was decent quality, fun to read again. thanks!
